	them all atomically so they're only calculated once and can return
	consistent results.

	* camel-folder.h: Added CAMEL_FOLDER_DELETED, CAMEL_FOLDER_JUNKED,
	and CAMEL_FOLDER_VISIBLE args, to support client display of
	various values.

