	* camel-mime-part.h: Revert previous changes.

	* camel-mime-part-utils.c: Revert previous changes.

	* camel-data-wrapper.c (camel_data_wrapper_init): Revert previous
	changes.
	(write_to_stream): Revert previous changes.

